::Whistler::
    He wakes up and looks around confused as to where he is.  Then he 
remembers going to the conference room.  He whistles "Wow sure did get busy 
in here."  He cracks his neck, stands up from his seat and walks too the far 
corner where he could watch what was going on without being seen.
